title: Did someone say that Wukang can't jungle in Season 5?
body:
I'm sorry, i didn't hear you over me LEGENDARY ZED BITCHES! Ohh yyeeeeaaaaaa!

< This guy got him 4 free kills by the 10 minute mark and had a map presence that was far greater than a post 6 WW's.

WuKang is the KIIINNNNGGG of the jungle!
